description: Young people who have just got their college diploma sometimes suffer from an inflated ego. This guy was a prime example. He got his bachelor degree in management and started looking for a well-paid job. When he realized there are no companies fighting over him, he visited our agency seeking help. The boy was nice and very like-able but for someone who never had a full-time job, his demands were not exactly small. And he was so annoying! He asked and moaned constantly. He didn´t like the camera, the job, the fee... I was surprised he didn´t complain about my proposition and took his clothes off almost instantly. Maybe because he had absolutely nothing to be embarrassed about. His body was superb in every aspect.
title: Dirty Scout 66
